enregistrements, quotas API</td>\n</tr>\n<tr data-start=\"10065\" data-end=\"10242\">\n<td data-start=\"10065\" data-end=\"10087\" data-col-size=\"sm\"><strong data-start=\"10067\" data-end=\"10086\">MVP marketplace</strong></td>\n<td data-start=\"10087\" data-end=\"10120\" data-col-size=\"sm\">Bubble + Stripe Connect + Make</td>\n<td data-start=\"10120\" data-end=\"10167\" data-col-size=\"md\">Plan app, ex&eacute;cutions sc&eacute;narios, frais Stripe</td>\n<td data-start=\"10167\" data-end=\"10200\" data-col-size=\"sm\"><strong data-start=\"10169\" data-end=\"10182\">150&ndash;500 &euro;</strong> (+ frais Stripe)</td>\n<td data-start=\"10200\" data-end=\"10242\" data-col-size=\"md\">KYC, litiges, volum&eacute;trie des paiements</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p data-start=\"10244\" data-end=\"10332\">* indicatif, d&eacute;pend du trafic, du nombre d&rsquo;utilisateurs et du volume d&rsquo;automatisations.</p>\n<hr data-start=\"10334\" data-end=\"10337\">\n<h2 data-start=\"10339\" data-end=\"10382\">Mini cas r&eacute;el (fictionnel mais r&eacute;aliste)</h2>\n<blockquote data-start=\"10384\" data-end=\"10493\">\n<p data-start=\"10386\" data-end=\"10493\"><strong data-start=\"10386\" data-end=\"10397\">Briefer</strong> : une startup B2B veut <strong data-start=\"10421\" data-end=\"10447\">vendre des prestations</strong> et g&eacute;n&eacute;rer des leads qualifi&eacute;s en 2 semaines.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul data-start=\"10495\" data-end=\"11056\">\n<li data-start=\"10495\" data-end=\"10619\">\n<p data-start=\"10497\" data-end=\"10619\"><strong data-start=\"10497\" data-end=\"10510\">Semaine 1</strong> : landing + blog sur Webflow, formulaires reli&eacute;s &agrave; Airtable, sc&eacute;nario Make &rarr; Slack &amp; CRM, newsletter auto.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"10620\" data-end=\"10754\">\n<p data-start=\"10622\" data-end=\"10754\"><strong data-start=\"10622\" data-end=\"10635\">Semaine 2</strong> : mini-portail client Softr (d&eacute;p&ocirc;t de documents, suivi), 3 automatisations (relances, digest hebdo, scoring simple).</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"10755\" data-end=\"10926\">\n<p data-start=\"10757\" data-end=\"10926\"><strong data-start=\"10757\" data-end=\"10775\">R&eacute;sultats 30 j</strong> : 3 pages piliers rank&eacute;es sur des requ&ecirc;tes <em data-start=\"10819\" data-end=\"10829\">mid-tail</em>, 120 leads capt&eacute;s, temps d&rsquo;onboarding client <strong data-start=\"10875\" data-end=\"10891\">divis&eacute; par 2</strong> (automatisation des checklists).</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"10927\" data-end=\"11056\">\n<p data-start=\"10929\" data-end=\"11056\"><strong data-start=\"10929\" data-end=\"10938\">Le&ccedil;on</strong> : on a privil&eacute;gi&eacute; l&rsquo;<strong data-start=\"10959\" data-end=\"10972\">it&eacute;ration</strong> (MVP robuste) et <strong data-start=\"10990\" data-end=\"11009\">l&rsquo;observabilit&eacute;</strong> (logs + alertes) avant d&rsquo;ajouter des features.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"11058\" data-end=\"11061\">\n<h2 data-start=\"11063\" data-end=\"11099\">Checklist de lancement (&agrave; cocher)</h2>\n<ul class=\"contains-task-list\" data-start=\"11101\" data-end=\"11635\">\n<li class=\"task-list-item\" data-start=\"11101\" data-end=\"11134\">\n<p data-start=\"11107\" data-end=\"11134\"><input disabled=\"disabled\" type=\"checkbox\"> Objectifs &amp; KPI chiffr&eacute;s.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\" data-start=\"11135\" data-end=\"11193\">\n<p data-start=\"11141\" data-end=\"11193\"><input disabled=\"disabled\" type=\"checkbox\"> Mod&egrave;le de donn&eacute;es (entit&eacute;s/relations/permissions).</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\" data-start=\"11194\" data-end=\"11233\">\n<p data-start=\"11200\" data-end=\"11233\"><input disabled=\"disabled\" type=\"checkbox\"> Maquettes du parcours critique.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\" data-start=\"11234\" data-end=\"11290\">\n<p data-start=\"11236\" data-end=\"11290\"><input disabled=\"disabled\" type=\"checkbox\"> <strong data-start=\"11240\" data-end=\"11258\">Stack minimale</strong> valid&eacute;e (front, data, iPaaS).</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\" data-start=\"11291\" data-end=\"11337\">\n<p data-start=\"11297\" data-end=\"11337\"><input disabled=\"disabled\" type=\"checkbox\"> POC en sandbox + 5 tests utilisateurs.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\" data-start=\"11338\" data-end=\"11384\">\n<p data-start=\"11344\" data-end=\"11384\"><input disabled=\"disabled\" type=\"checkbox\"> R&ocirc;les/permissions + DPA sign&eacute;s (RGPD).</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\" data-start=\"11385\" data-end=\"11420\">\n<p data-start=\"11391\" data-end=\"11420\"><input disabled=\"disabled\" type=\"checkbox\"> Exports/Backups programm&eacute;s.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\" data-start=\"11421\" data-end=\"11472\">\n<p data-start=\"11427\" data-end=\"11472\"><input disabled=\"disabled\" type=\"checkbox\"> Sc&eacute;narios d&eacute;coup&eacute;s + <strong data-start=\"11448\" data-end=\"11459\">retries</strong> + alertes.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\" data-start=\"11473\" data-end=\"11528\">\n<p data-start=\"11479\" data-end=\"11528\"><input disabled=\"disabled\" type=\"checkbox\"> SEO : titles/meta, images compress&eacute;es, JSON-LD.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\" data-start=\"11529\" data-end=\"11563\">\n<p data-start=\"11535\" data-end=\"11563\"><input disabled=\"disabled\" type=\"checkbox\"> Analytics &amp; logs en place.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\" data-start=\"11564\" data-end=\"11594\">\n<p data-start=\"11566\" data-end=\"11594\"><input disabled=\"disabled\" type=\"checkbox\"> <strong data-start=\"11570\" data-end=\"11581\">Runbook</strong> incidents.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\" data-start=\"11595\" data-end=\"11635\">\n<p data-start=\"11601\" data-end=\"11635\"><input disabled=\"disabled\" type=\"checkbox\"> Roadmap d&rsquo;it&eacute;rations (S, S+1, M1).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"11637\" data-end=\"11640\">\n<h2 data-start=\"11642\" data-end=\"11668\">Appels &agrave; l&rsquo;action (CTA)</h2>\n<ul data-start=\"11670\" data-end=\"11910\">\n<li data-start=\"11670\" data-end=\"11741\">\n<p data-start=\"11672\" data-end=\"11741\"><strong data-start=\"11672\" data-end=\"11711\">Recevoir la checklist nocode en PDF</strong> (1 page, pr&ecirc;te &agrave; imprimer).</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"11742\" data-end=\"11839\">\n<p data-start=\"11744\" data-end=\"11839\"><strong data-start=\"11744\" data-end=\"11782\">Demander un audit gratuit de stack</strong> (30 min) pour r&eacute;duire co&ucirc;ts &amp; augmenter time-to-value.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"11840\" data-end=\"11910\">\n<p data-start=\"11842\" data-end=\"11910\"><strong data-start=\"11842\" data-end=\"11888\">Voir notre comparatif d&rsquo;outils nocode 2025</strong> (tableau interactif).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-start=\"15300\" data-end=\"15812\">Le <strong data-start=\"15303\" data-end=\"15313\">nocode</strong> n&rsquo;est plus un plan B : c&rsquo;est une <strong data-start=\"15347\" data-end=\"15368\">strat&eacute;gie produit</strong>. En combinant une <strong data-start=\"15387\" data-end=\"15405\">stack minimale</strong>, la m&eacute;thode <strong data-start=\"15418\" data-end=\"15434\">R.A.P.I.D.E.</strong>, une <strong data-start=\"15440\" data-end=\"15462\">gouvernance l&eacute;g&egrave;re</strong> (r&ocirc;les, backups, logs) et des <strong data-start=\"15493\" data-end=\"15501\">KPIs</strong> clairs, vous livrez en <strong data-start=\"15525\" data-end=\"15534\">jours</strong> ce qui prenait des <strong data-start=\"15554\" data-end=\"15562\">mois</strong> &mdash; sans sacrifier qualit&eacute;, s&eacute;curit&eacute; ni SEO. Commencez petit, <strong data-start=\"15623\" data-end=\"15634\">mesurez</strong>, it&eacute;rez. Quand un module d&eacute;passe le cadre, <strong data-start=\"15678\" data-end=\"15694\">d&eacute;crochez-le</strong> vers du code ou un service d&eacute;di&eacute;. C&rsquo;est cette approche hybride, pragmatique, qui d&eacute;livre un <strong data-start=\"15787\" data-end=\"15796\">20/20</strong> sur le terrain.</p>\n<p data-start=\"15300\" data-end=\"15812\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h2 data-start=\"11917\" data-end=\"11931\">FAQ express</h2>\n<p data-start=\"11933\" data-end=\"12117\"><strong data-start=\"11933\" data-end=\"11971\">Le nocode remplace-t-il les devs ?</strong><br data-start=\"11971\" data-end=\"11974\">Non. Il <strong data-start=\"11982\" data-end=\"11994\">r&eacute;alloue</strong> leur temps vers les parties complexes : API, s&eacute;curit&eacute;, performance, scalabilit&eacute;. Les &eacute;quipes non-tech s&rsquo;occupent du reste.</p>\n<p data-start=\"12119\" data-end=\"12312\"><strong data-start=\"12119\" data-end=\"12154\">Peut-on scaler une app nocode ?</strong><br data-start=\"12154\" data-end=\"12157\">Oui, si vous <strong data-start=\"12170\" data-end=\"12189\">mesurez l&rsquo;usage</strong>, <strong data-start=\"12191\" data-end=\"12217\">d&eacute;coupez les workflows</strong>, mettez en place du <strong data-start=\"12238\" data-end=\"12249\">caching</strong> et pr&eacute;voyez une <strong data-start=\"12266\" data-end=\"12284\">voie de sortie</strong> pour les modules gourmands.</p>\n<p data-start=\"12314\" data-end=\"12603\"><strong data-start=\"12314\" data-end=\"12357\">Et la s&eacute;curit&eacute;/compliance (RGPD, KYC) ?</strong><br data-start=\"12357\" data-end=\"12360\">Traitez le nocode comme un produit logiciel classique : r&ocirc;les, journaux, sauvegardes, p&eacute;n-tests, <strong data-start=\"12457\" data-end=\"12464\">DPA</strong>. Pour les <strong data-start=\"12475\" data-end=\"12491\">marketplaces</strong>, d&eacute;l&eacute;guez le <strong data-start=\"12505\" data-end=\"12512\">KYC</strong> et les obligations de paiement &agrave; <strong data-start=\"12546\" data-end=\"12564\">Stripe Connect</strong>. <span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span cla